Some tricycle (Keke) and motorcycle (Okada) riders in Lagos State, were spotted in a viral video being loaded in a lorry for a trip to an unknown destination. A man was heard saying in the background that “Kekes are going, they are leaving Lagos”, while recording the video. CACOL worries over Lagos ban on Okada, Tricycle in parts of state, describes action as hasty Vanguard reports that the truck loaded with motorbikes waa spotted on Friday night leaving the Ijegun-Satelite for North. Watch the video below, sourced from YouTube.